### Omega Connect API Test Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code
### Or import into Postman/Insomnia

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION ROUTES
### ============================================

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "gender": "male",
  "bio": "Hello, I'm a test user!",
  "interests": ["music", "sports", "travel"]
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Password
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/updatepassword
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### ============================================
### USER ROUTES
### ============================================

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bio": "Updated bio - I love coding!",
  "interests": ["coding", "music", "travel", "photography"],
  "gender": "male"
}

### Get Recommendations (Live Users)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/recommendations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Swipe User - Like
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/swipe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439011",
  "action": "like"
}

### Swipe User - Skip
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/swipe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439011",
  "action": "skip"
}

### Report User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/report
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439011",
  "action": "report",
  "reason": "Inappropriate behavior"
}

### Block User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/report
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "507f1f77bcf86cd799439011",
  "action": "block"
}

### Get User Matches
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/matches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### VIDEO ROUTES
### ============================================

### Start Live Stream
POST {{baseUrl}}/video/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Join Stream
POST {{baseUrl}}/video/join
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "streamKey": "user_id_1234567890_abc123def456"
}

### End Stream
POST {{baseUrl}}/video/end
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "streamKey": "user_id_1234567890_abc123def456"
}

### Get Stream Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/status/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Stream History
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### SUBSCRIPTION ROUTES
### ============================================

### Get Subscription Plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription/plans

### Get Subscription Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscription/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Subscribe to Premium
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/subscribe
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plan": "premium",
  "paymentMethodId": "pm_1234567890"
}

### Cancel Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscription/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

